 from frank marvin contex com frank perdicaro subject hawk gt new seat review keywords corbin lines three zero unable to stand the pain anymore my wife bought the corbin gunfighter and lady with passenger backrest for my hawk gt it came with no instructions but it came two weeks earlier than they said it would installation would have been very easy but the seat fastening hardware was apparently always on the wrong sides with the stock seat it never was easy to put on once i figured that out the new seat went on the first try the passenger backrest though does not fit as i thought it might the supplied screw to set the backrest angle does not fit and i have not yet found a suitable hard sae grade eight or perhaps five one four two zero bolt that fits there is a a soft bolt in there now just don t lean back the driver s section of the seat is a bit wider seems comfortable enough but then again i put about five zero zero zero miles on the stock seat without a thought the passenger s section has about eight times the volume of foam that the stock seat has and from my short test it seems much more comfortable the backrest helps a bit but i ve not has enough time to really test it the backrest also comes with a small pocket its now more difficult to swing my leg up over the one zero taller seat if i go on the three notch ride soon dixville pinkham smugglers i ll give a more complete report but in general it seems like an improvement frank evan perdicaro xyvision color systems legalize guns drugs and cash today one zero one edgewater drive inhouse frank marvin x five five seven two wakefield ma outhouse frank contex com six one seven two four five four one zero zero x five five seven two zero one eight eight zero one two eight five